      <title>肯尼亚提出回购 20 亿美元债券的要约；收益率暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/kenya-opens-tender-offer-for-maturing-eurobonds-yields-plummet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚政府提出回购 6 月份到期的 20 亿美元欧元债券，并宣布计划发行新债。 2024年证券的收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/kenya-opens-tender-offer-for-maturing-eurobonds-yields-plummet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NYCB 股价跌至 27 年低点后未能安抚投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nycb-stock-turns-positive-after-bank-says-deposits-have-climbed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 的股价周二触及 27 年来的新低，在公司高管试图向投资者保证其财务状况强劲后，该公司股价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nycb-stock-turns-positive-after-bank-says-deposits-have-climbed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 Milei 改革回到原点，阿根廷债券暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/argentina-bonds-dip-as-milei-s-reforms-sent-back-to-square-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷执政联盟意识到自己没有足够的票数来推动总统哈维尔·米莱的改革方案在众议院获得通过，随后将其重新提交国会审议，导致阿根廷债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/argentina-bonds-dip-as-milei-s-reforms-sent-back-to-square-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷调整薪酬计划，计划回购高达 14 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正在彻底改革其向交易撮合者付款的方式，以便为股东释放更稳定的现金流，并批准了一项回购高达 14 亿美元股票的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行业领跌，欧洲股市小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对银行面临新兴商业地产问题的担忧以及央行官员削弱了提前降息的希望，欧洲股市在下午交易中小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/european-stocks-steady-as-traders-weigh-earnings-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
